<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/4939005.Rajiv_Malhotra"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1308918062p3/4939005.jpg);'></div>
